author: Alex Norcia, Maxwell Strachan
title: FDA Admits There’s Actually No Evidence Vaping Makes COVID-19 Worse
description: The federal agency had previously stated that vapers were at an elevated risk of developing complications tied to COVID-19.
content: The Food and Drug Administration (FDA) has backtracked on its previous hardline position on vaping and the coronavirus, saying on Wednesday that there is no known evidence that vaping put an individual at higher risk of developing complications tied to COVID-… [+3712 chars]
